8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Crello and Tome share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Collaboration. On the other hand, Tome uniquely offers Ai Generation and Responsive, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Crello holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Tome scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Crello and Tome offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Crello's free tier and Tome's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
